331
00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:50,239
[SPEAKER_00] I znate li kako se to dogodilo?

332
00:36:50,800 --> 00:36:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] Možete li možda dati savjet, savjet nekome tko sada sluša?

333
00:36:58,480 --> 00:36:59,679
